  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors evaluated under ASME V&V 40-2018. Submitted under Minimal profile; context of use scope is not formally bound in this package.",
