    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Package accepted for registry under Minimal profile. Thirteen credibility factors have been populated with required and achieved levels. Six factors remain not-assessed due to epistemic gaps at MRL 5; seven factors assessed all show achieved levels below required levels. Full decision on model fitness for VAD regulatory submission is deferred pending completion of missing assessments.",
